    <h3 itemprop="headline">Tesla Shareholders Approve $44.9 Billion Pay Package for Elon Musk, Show Confidence in Leadership</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Tesla shareholders vote to restore CEO Elon Musk's pay package after a Delaware judge threw it out earlier this year, sending a strong message of support for his leadership of the electric vehicle maker.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/14/future-of-elon-musk-and-tesla-are-on-the-line-as-shareholders-vote-on-massive-pay-package/"  >(TOM KRISHER and DAVID HAMILTON, Associated Press, KLAS, CBS News)</a>
