    <h3 itemprop="headline">Lynn Conway, microchip pioneer who overcame transgender discrimination, dies at 86</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Lynn Conway, a pioneer in the design of microchips that are at the heart of consumer electronics who overcame discrimination as a transgender person, has died at age 86.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/14/lynn-conway-microchip-pioneer-who-overcame-transgender-discrimination-dies-at-86/"  >(ED WHITE, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
