    <h3 itemprop="headline">Detroit Pistons fire coach Monty Williams after one season that ended with NBA's worst record</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Detroit Pistons have fired coach Monty Williams after just one season that ended with an NBA-worst 14-68 record.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/19/pistons-fire-coach-monty-williams-after-one-season-ap-source-says/"  >(Tim Reynolds, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
