    <h3 itemprop="headline">Sources: Cardinals to call up Magnolia HS grad pitcher Adam Kloffenstein</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The St. Louis Cardinals are expected to call up right-handed pitcher Adam Kloffenstein, multiple sources tell KPRC 2. Kloffenstein is a 2018 3rd round draft pick out of Magnolia High School to the Toronto Blue Jays.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/19/sources-cardinals-to-call-up-magnolia-hs-grad-pitcher-adam-kloffenstein/"  >(Ari Alexander, KPRC 2)</a>
