    <h3 itemprop="headline">Rowdies' Herivaux makes return after injury-riddled season</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Zachary Herivaux has been playing soccer since he was 5 years old. He says being out on the pitch brings him peace. So, when the game that he loves was taken away from him more than a year, it was one of the most challenging chapters of his life.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/19/rowdies-herivaux-makes-return-after-injury-riddled-season/"  >(Kenny Morales, WFLA, NBC)</a>
