           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump campaign says he will stay in Milwaukee for GOP convention, not at Chicago property</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Former President Trump will stay in Milwaukee for the upcoming Republican National Convention, his campaign confirmed, batting down reports the former president intended to spend the night at his Chicago property and commute to the Wisconsin city for the event.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/19/trump-campaign-says-he-will-stay-in-milwaukee-for-gop-convention-not-at-chicago-property/"  >(Brett Samuels, NewsNation)</a>
